<chapter id="Message_Inquiry"> 
<title>Message Inquiry</title>

    <section condition="TITLE=Cash Services: Message Inquiry" id="MI" role="TOPIC">
      <title>Message Inquiry - List</title>

      <para role="TEXT">After selecting the <emphasis role="bold">Message
      Inquiry</emphasis> option from the <emphasis>Cash Services</emphasis>
      &gt; <emphasis>File</emphasis> page, list of all messages sent for
      authorised Entities, will be displayed.<indexterm>
          <primary>Message Inquiry</primary>

          <secondary>listing messages</secondary>
        </indexterm><indexterm>
          <primary>Helpdesk Message Inquiry</primary>
        </indexterm></para>

      <para role="TEXT"><graphic fileref="../images/CUG_Cash_Services_file_message.jpg"
      width="160mm"/></para>

      <para role="TEXT">Click on the <emphasis role="bold">Search
      Options</emphasis> link to display a list of search criteria fields that
      can be used to filter. These are <guilabel moreinfo="none">BIB
      Ref</guilabel> or <guilabel moreinfo="none">Entity</guilabel> field.
      The list is not displayed until search criteria are entered and
      <emphasis role="bold">Search</emphasis> is clicked. To display all
      records, enter an asterisk in any of the criteria fields.</para>

      <para role="TEXT">The columns returned contains the following
      information:</para>

      <section role="ITEM">
        <title>New Form - General Details</title>

        <informaltable role="TEXT">
          <tgroup cols="2">
            <colspec colname="c1" colwidth="2.0*"/>

            <colspec colname="c2" colwidth="8.0*"/>

            <thead>
              <row>
                <entry valign="top"><para role="TEXT">Field</para></entry>

                <entry valign="top"><para role="TEXT">Description</para></entry>
              </row>
            </thead>

            <tbody>
              <row>
                <entry valign="top"><para role="TEXT"> <guilabel moreinfo="none">BIB
                Ref</guilabel> </para></entry>

                <entry valign="top"><para role="TEXT">The Unique reference number
                generated by <xi:include href="../entities_en.xml"
                xpointer="ent_appli"
                xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude"/> for this file,
                when it was initiated.</para></entry>
              </row>

              <row>
                <entry valign="top"><guilabel role="bold"> Entity</guilabel></entry>

                <entry valign="top"><para role="TEXT">The Entity this message was sent
                on behalf of.</para></entry>
              </row>

              <row>
                <entry valign="top"><para role="TEXT"> <guilabel
                moreinfo="none">Topic</guilabel> </para></entry>

                <entry valign="top"><para role="TEXT">The topic of this
                message</para></entry>
              </row>

              <row>
                <entry valign="top"><para role="TEXT"> <guilabel
                moreinfo="none">Input</guilabel> </para></entry>

                <entry valign="top"><para role="TEXT">The date the message was
                sent</para></entry>
              </row>
            </tbody>
          </tgroup>
        </informaltable>

        <para role="TEXT">Each record is shown with one or more of the
        following action icons to the left of the entry, depending on its
        status:</para>

        <informaltable role="TEXT">
          <tgroup cols="2">
            <colspec colname="c1" colwidth="2.0*"/>

            <colspec colname="c2" colwidth="8.0*"/>

            <thead>
              <row>
                <entry valign="top"><para role="TEXT">Symbol</para></entry>

                <entry valign="top"><para role="TEXT">Description</para></entry>
              </row>
            </thead>

            <tbody>
              <row>
                <entry valign="top"><para role="TEXT"> <inlinemediaobject>
                    <imageobject>
                      <imagedata fileref="../images/icon_view.jpg"
                                 role="ICON_LOCK" width="4mm"/>
                    </imageobject>
                  </inlinemediaobject> </para></entry>

                <entry valign="top"><para role="TEXT">Click to open a popup window
                displaying the current master details of the
                record.</para></entry>
              </row>

              <row>
                <entry valign="top"><para role="TEXT"> <inlinemediaobject>
                    <imageobject>
                      <imagedata fileref="../images/icon_history.jpg"
                                 role="ICON_LOCK" width="4mm"/>
                    </imageobject>
                  </inlinemediaobject> </para></entry>

                <entry valign="top"><para role="TEXT">Click to display a history list of
                all events for the record, detailing the complete history of
                the file. For each event in the life of the file, the list
                shows the <guilabel moreinfo="none">Release Date</guilabel>,
                the <guilabel moreinfo="none">Type</guilabel> of the event,
                the <guilabel moreinfo="none">Status</guilabel>, the <guilabel
                moreinfo="none">Currency</guilabel> and transaction <guilabel
                moreinfo="none">Amount</guilabel> (e.g. the Purchase Order
                amount), and the Entities of the input and supervising
                users.</para></entry>
              </row>
            </tbody>
          </tgroup>
        </informaltable>
      </section>
    </section>
</chapter>
